      <name>Harise</name>
      <description><![CDATA[<strong>Harise</strong><br/>Kyoto / Kyoto<br/>Cuisine: Japanese, Kaiseki, Washoku<br/>Reservation: Book Instantly<br/>Dinner range: $$$ JPY 10k-20k<br/>Dinner: JPY 13,950 - 31,625<br/>Lunch range: $$ JPY 5k-10k<br/>Lunch: JPY 6,050 - 10,120<br/>Summary: A beloved Kyoto institution that has been in business for over 350 years, famous for its eccentric local cuisine, especially its variety of dishes incorporating soups, and for its dedication in catering to each customer’s preferences.<br/><a href="https://pocket-concierge.jp/en/restaurants/244008/?extlink=va-jp-ICS-GMS_LP_en" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Pocket Concierge</a><br/>Approximate location based on public geocoding unless replaced by stronger source matching.]]></description>
